PrecisAuthority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a CONVENTION on the RECOGNITION AND ENFORCEMENT OF JUDGMENTS IN CIVIL AND COMMERCIAL MATTERS AND ON MUTUAL LEGAL ASSISTANCE IN MAINTENANCE with the FRENCH REPUBLIC, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing either the Hon. Allan Rock, the Hon. Pierre Pettigrew, Gordon S. Smith, or Jean-Pierre Juneau to sign the said Convention.

precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a CONVENTION on
the RECOGNITION AND ENFORCEMENT OF JUDGMENTS IN CIVIL AND COMMERCIAL
MATTERS AND ON MUTUAL LEGAL ASSISTANCE IN MAINTENANCE with the FRENCH

the Hon. Allan Rock, the Hon. Pierre Pettigrew, Gordon S. Smith, or
